data.description: The beautiful Juliet shines from the moment you lay your eyes on it. This humble 3-bedroom abode is perfect for you and your growing family. An open floor plan provides views from the kitchen to the dining room and into the living room making entertaining a breeze. Tucked in the back allowing privacy is the fabulous master suite boasting a large bathroom with a walk-in closet. What else could you need? How about a spacious bonus room upstairs with enough area for a pool table or full stadium seating for a theater room. The remaining two bedrooms are perfect for guest rooms or a home office. The Juliet is welcoming and perfect for you and your loved ones. Don't forget to ask about our great packages! Call Sales Rep for Closing Cost Assistance.
